      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2">✓</span>
        <span>Longer-lasting than shaving</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <ul class="space-y-2">
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2">✓</span>
        <span>No razor burn or cuts</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2">✓</span>
        <span>Removes peach fuzz</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-center">
        <span class="text-purple-600 mr-2">✓</span>
        <span>Gentle on sensitive skin</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">The Process</h2>

<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <ol class="space-y-4">
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">1.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Consultation</strong> — We assess your skin and discuss any sensitivities or concerns.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">2.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Cleansing</strong> — Your face is thoroughly cleansed to remove makeup and oils.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">3.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Protection</strong> — We apply powder to protect your skin and help the wax adhere properly.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">4.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Waxing</strong> — Using gentle hard wax, we carefully remove hair from each area.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">5.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Soothing</strong> — Calming products are applied to reduce any redness.
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Before Your Appointment</h2>

<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <ul class="space-y-2">
    <li>• Avoid retinol or exfoliating products for 5-7 days</li>
    <li>• Stop using Accutane at least 6 months before waxing</li>
    <li>• Avoid sun exposure for 24 hours before</li>
    <li>• Come with clean skin (no makeup)</li>
    <li>• Let hair grow to at least ¼ inch</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Aftercare</h2>

<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <ul class="space-y-2">
    <li>• Avoid touching your face for 24 hours</li>
    <li>• No makeup for 12-24 hours</li>
    <li>• Avoid sun exposure and use SPF</li>
    <li>• Skip exfoliating for 3 days</li>
    <li>• Avoid saunas and hot showers for 24 hours</li>
  </ul>
</div>

